OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782582478
OL,3,CBloody Sunday family felt 'anxious and
OL,4,Cwary' after menacing message
OL,6,FSpeaking to UTV, Mickey McKinney said
OL,7,Fanybody should be allowed to campaign
OL,8,Ffor justice without feeling in danger.
OL,10,FPortis, of Olive Street in Belfast,
OL,11,Fdenied two counts of improper use of a
OL,12,Fpublic communications network to send
OL,13,Fa message of a menacing character.
OL,15,FBut in April he was found guilty of
OL,16,Fboth offences following a contest at
OL,17,FBelfast Magistrates' Court.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
