OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782582478
OL,3,CBloody Sunday family felt 'anxious and
OL,4,Cwary' after menacing message
OL,6,FProsecutors said Portis targeted the
OL,7,Fbrothers on September 18 and October
OL,8,F22 last year during the high profile
OL,9,FSoldier F trial.
OL,11,FThe former member of the Parachute
OL,12,FRegiment was accused but ultimately
OL,13,Ffound not guilty of murdering 26-year-
OL,14,Fold William McKinney on Bloody Sunday.
OL,16,FMr McKinney was among 13 people shot
OL,17,Fdead when troops opened fire on civil
OL,18,Frights demonstrators in Derry's
OL,19,FBogside on January 30, 1972.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
