OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782582478
OL,3,CBloody Sunday family felt 'anxious and
OL,4,Cwary' after menacing message
OL,6,FPolice were alerted to a Facebook
OL,7,Fposting allegedly attributed to
OL,8,FPortis, who also uses the name Dean
OL,9,FMartin, early on in Soldier F's trial.
OL,11,FA menancing message was placed above a
OL,12,Fnewspaper report and photograph of Mr
OL,13,FMcKinney's three brothers, Joe, Mickey
OL,14,Fand John, attending the hearing in
OL,15,FBelfast.
OL,17,FPortis insisted the message was not
OL,18,Fdirected at or about the brothers,
OL,19,Finstead claiming his intention was
OL,20,Fonly about creating a platform for
OL,21,Fdebate.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
