OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782582478
OL,3,CBloody Sunday family felt 'anxious and
OL,4,Cwary' after menacing message
OL,6,FBut in witness statements the three
OL,7,Fcomplainants described being left in a
OL,8,Fstate of fear they were being watched
OL,9,Fand potentially under threat.
OL,11,FMickey McKinney said the brothers were
OL,12,Fleaving Derry to travel to Belfast and
OL,13,Fgetting the threat "wasn't a nice
OL,14,Ffeeling".
OL,16,F"We didn't know who made the threat,
OL,17,Fand I was certainly very anxious about
OL,18,Fit.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782582478
OL,3,CBloody Sunday family felt 'anxious and
OL,4,Cwary' after menacing message
OL,6,F"We're quite glad, he's got his days,
OL,7,Fand hopefully this guy will learn now
OL,8,Ffrom what he's done`that you just
OL,9,Fcan't go around threatening people,
OL,10,Fthreatening to kill people, when
OL,11,Fthey're attending a trial.
OL,13,F"Anybody chasing justice for what
OL,14,Fhappened in the reality of it has
OL,15,Fevery right to do so, no matter who
OL,16,Fthey are. They should be left alone to
OL,17,Fdo it."
OL,19,FJoe McKinney said he was "very wary".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
