PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782582478
OL,3,CBloody Sunday family felt 'anxious and
OL,4,Cwary' after menacing message
OL,6,F"You would be careful, sort of looking
OL,7,Fover your shoulder type of thing.
OL,9,F"I think it's unfortunate that anybody
OL,10,Fgets themselves into that situation,
OL,11,Fespecially one, I would imagine, whose
OL,12,Fknowledge of Bloody Sunday and what
OL,13,Fhappened is fairly limited, whenever
OL,14,Fhe came out with such a statement."
OL,16,FJohn McKinney expressed concerns that
OL,17,Fthe postings could have been made by a
OL,18,Fdangerous and violent individual.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
