OL,3,CBloody Sunday family felt 'anxious and
OL,4,Cwary' after menacing message
OL,6,F"I am worried for myself and my
OL,7,Ffamily's safety since seeing this," he
OL,8,Fstated.
OL,10,F"I have fear that I am being watched
OL,11,Fand followed. I take this threat
OL,12,Fseriously and fear that something
OL,13,Fcould happen."
OL,15,FSentencing Portis, Deputy District
OL,16,FJudge John Rea imposed three months
OL,17,Fcustody for the offences.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@cO]rD@AOUuD@NO]
