OL,3,CBloody Sunday family felt 'anxious and
OL,4,Cwary' after menacing message
OL,6,FHe also activated a previous suspended
OL,7,Fterm and ordered the defendant to
OL,8,Fserve a further three months behind
OL,9,Fbars.
OL,11,FUnder the terms of the two-year
OL,12,Frestraining order, Portis is also
OL,13,Fforbidden from pestering the brothers
OL,14,For journalist Hugh Jordan.
OL,16,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,17,FITVX
OL,19,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,20,Fhere.
